{"tid":367490,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個同異性best friend 做過最癲嘅事","createTime":"2017-08-20T18:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T04:27:26.000Z","uid":135762,"like":44,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65fbc5541d4dcecc6c53b12e56a5f3b3dc922649","tid":367490,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:09:48.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講扑嘢 含撚啲變態嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我先 <br />\n之前單獨即興凌晨步行咗廿幾k<br />\n上夜山山頂睇日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住望住個太陽升起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋順帶一問<br />\n<br />\n你覺得男同女有冇純友誼？  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做到BFF<br />\n冇任何性關係嗰種  完全係心靈上嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4e4dfda6289f5730a88201afbe7ed51fd47f1e","tid":367490,"uid":102642,"like":5,"dislike":140,"score":-135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:29:03.000Z","msg":"想要個純友誼既女仔朋友<br />\ntg f999123"},{"pid":"76cb8fa808149ba1ad243b14af5d6bdad75dd613","tid":367490,"uid":128830,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:30:34.000Z","msg":"傾左成百個鐘電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df29b1479ffbd8eea945b74cb8837f02ad381911","tid":367490,"uid":24682,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"同兩個好frd既女仔同床一齊訓算唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：無扑到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個同樓主相似既<br />\n試過係外國凌晨1點幾，車個女仔上山睇夜景<br />\n之後有日前一晚食完飯話不如聽朝一齊睇日出<br />\n點知真係四點幾call佢起身，揸45分鐘車上山睇日出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好既女仔frd試過係我生日夜晚11點幾買蛋糕衝黎我屋企同我慶祝，佢屋企